AI Description: Intel Compiler Runtime (rt32) is a runtime library for applications compiled with Intel Compiler. It provides necessary runtime support for applications compiled with Intel Compiler, including math functions, memory management, and threading support.
Core Features: Optimized Math Functions For Intel Hardware, Memory Management Support, Threading Support For Parallel Execution
General Tags: Runtime Library, Intel Compiler, Optimized Math Functions, Threading Support
